PRIVACY POLICY FOR MOBILE APPLICATION
Show to me

This privacy policy governs your use of the software application Show to me (“Application”) for mobile devices that was created by Artem Berdnikov. The Application is Basic description of the app (features, functionality and content)

User Provided Information
The Application obtains only your email and nick name for identification you as user. With this Application you can shoot videos. Videos are deleted automatically and are not stored anywhere after the expiration of the video order. All of data is use only for this Application. We may also use the information you provided us to contact your from time to time to provide you with important information, required notices and marketing promotions.

Automatically Collected Information
The Application automatically obtains precise real time location information of the device only if Application active. This geo position is needed only to make a video and show orders for video near your geo position. The Application does not collect any additional user data.
